Package no.ntnu.idatx1005

Class MainApp

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
no.ntnu.idatx1005.MainApp
public class MainApp extends javafx.application.Application

Main application class for the application.

The main application class extends the Application class. It is responsible for initializing the database connection and creating the main view, as well as showing the appropriate views based on user input.

Since:
V0.1.0
Author:
Tord Fosse, William Holtsdalen
